description: The winter time is so homie and sad at the same time. I try to make my home more cozy, lay down and watch some TV series. It's too cold outside. At the same time I think I should make more, maybe I should make more connections with the local art community, so maybe it will make me more alive in this winter time. But I stay at home when I have a chance. And I play with my kids and watch some movies and tv series and read the books slowly.
